<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=7,8,edge" />
<meta http-equiv="refresh" content="text/html;charset=UTF-8" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Shalimar&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="../styles/global.css" />
<link rel="stylesheet" href="../styles/index/index.css" />
<script src="https://unpkg.com/masonry-layout@4/dist/masonry.pkgd.min.js"></script>
<script defer type="module" src="../js/global.js"></script>
<script defer src="../js/index/index.js"></script>
<title>Soap Works</title>
</head>
<body>
<%- include("../partials/Header/Header.ejs") %>
<h1 class="heading">Soap Works</h1>
<p class="intro">
Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Velit qui quam nobis facilis ex necessitatibus optio harum laudantium eos repellat? Suscipit libero ullam adipisci. Mollitia alias nulla voluptas tempora distinctio!
</p>
<h2>Soaps</h2>
<section class="soaps">
<%soaps.forEach((soap) => {
%>
<div class="grid-item">
<img src="<%=soap.ImageUrl%>" alt="<%=soap.Title%>" />
<h2><%=soap.Title%></h2>
<p>
$<%=soap.Price%>
</p>
</div>
<%})%>
</section>
<section class="hidden soap-hidden-section">
	<div class="soap-detail-container">
		<%soaps.forEach((soap)=> {
			%>
			<img src="<%=soap.ImageUrl%>" />
			<div class="descriptive-soap">
				<h2>
					<%=soap.Title%>
				</h2>
				<p class="descriptive-price">
					<%=soap.Price%>
				</p>
				<p class="description">
					<%=soap.Description%>
				</p>
				<ul class="ingredients">
					<%soap.Ingredients.forEach((ingredient)=> {
						%>
						<li>
							<%=ingredient%>
						</li>
						<% }) %>
				</ul>
				<div class="prev-next">
					<button class="prev">Prev</button>
					<button class="next">Next</button>
				</div>
			</div>
			<% })%>
	</div>
</section>
<h3 class="second-heading">Kits</h3>
<p class="intro">
Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Rerum nam impedit pariatur mollitia doloribus iure nesciunt architecto? Alias mollitia, qui quas eveniet tempora, quaerat quibusdam sed, nihil non et asperiores!
</p>
<h2>Kit Selections</h2>
<section class="kits">
	<%kits.forEach((kit)=> {
		%>
		<div class="kit-item">
			<img src="<%=kit.ImageUrl%>" alt="<%=kit.Title%>" />
			<h2>
				<%=kit.Title%>
			</h2>
			<p>
				<%=kit.Quantity%> kits <br /> available
			</p>
		</div>
		<%})%>
</section>
</body>
</html>